lead_paragraph: Cristiano Ronaldo struck late to give Real Madrid a 2-1 victory in the 'Clasico' and ruin Barcelona's 39-game unbeaten run in a tense game overshadowed by debatable refereeing decisions on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Ronaldo Goal Hands Barca First Defeat in a Year
